  "task_id": "pico_echo.character.echo_idle_animation",
  "asset_name": "Echo animation: Idle",
  "category": "character",
  "subcategory": "echo",
  "description": "All Echo frames: frame canvas 40x40px, transparent background. No outlines. No shading. No gradients. No dithering. Colors: body #FFA300, cheek patch #FF004D, crest #FFEC27, beak/feet #AB5236, eyes #1D2B53. Echo occupies approx x=6..33,y=6..36 within the 40x40 canvas. Cheek patch is always present as a 3x3 block at x=24..26,y=18..20. Eyes are two 2x2 blocks at x=14..15,y=16..17 and x=22..23,y=16..17 unless the frame specifies eyes closed. Idle: 4 frames, FPS=2, loop=true. Frames: F1 eyes open, F2 eyes open with 1px crest sway to the right, F3 eyes closed (replace both eye blocks with a 4px horizontal line at y=17 from x=14..17 and x=22..25), F4 eyes open.",
